defs.docs:
This crate implements the [Unicode Bidirectional Algorithm][tr9] for display of mixed
 right-to-left and left-to-right text.  It is written in safe Rust, compatible with the
 current stable release.

defs.name: BidiClass
defs.value:
pub enum BidiClass {
    AL,
    AN,
    B,
    BN,
    CS,
    EN,
    ES,
    ET,
    FSI,
    L,
    LRE,
    LRI,
    LRO,
    NSM,
    ON,
    PDF,
    PDI,
    R,
    RLE,
    RLI,
    RLO,
    S,
    WS,
}
